{"tid":184341,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對死有恐懼","createTime":"2017-04-02T17:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T18:36:18.000Z","uid":86682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"787ddc461cc28a33e3c408a5629dc71708d59e38","tid":184341,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪小學開始<br />\n已經有好幾次親人離世要去殯儀館既經驗 <br />\n自始經常訓教一合埋眼<br />\n就會用左第三人稱視角去望住死左既自己訓左係棺材<br />\n果種孤寂<br />\n唔知點解會有好深刻感受<br />\n成日幻想將來我死既時候<br />\n所有想食既野 做既事 見既人<br />\n你死後都唔會再食到做到見到<br />\n<br />\n死左之後 個個都話死左就死左<br />\n唔會有任何感覺 咁大個人都未試過冇晒所有感覺<br />\n係永世都會冇晒 每日一合埋眼訓十個八個鐘就會起身就係第二日 而家你一死 就冇第二日出現 諗起都真係驚 又咁講 人人話死左就冇感覺 咁事實又係咪真呢 我訓果時又諗 如果死左之後其實係有感覺 只係你精神唔再控制到肉體 係會感覺到痛楚 係有意識既 咁未仲仆街 平時燒到隻手已經屌晒鬼 如果死後火化時真係有意識有感覺既 我真係唔敢去想像 每次一諗起就會出晒汗 訓唔著 諗起屋企人 好想叫佢地起身望多佢地幾眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0df37ae64d1e57c31cbb984f1068d030ecdcd98","tid":184341,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"推薦讀物<br />\nTuesdays with Morrie"},{"pid":"df138d6883937d1338daf6b7dfa7020c3613b1f5","tid":184341,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推薦讀物<br />\nTuesdays with Morrie</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90fd5c7e3dd812514519897673687fe19b1f7ae","tid":184341,"uid":8483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:46:47.000Z","msg":"之前有個中學同學過左身<br />\n個排都好驚死 差d有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808571d86a29af07c3574db8a9ed1c205c842810","tid":184341,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔驚死 但驚帶住遺憾咁死 會唔甘心同唔捨得"},{"pid":"4d6d24b9843f84623898c42ec1c98a77626e663b","tid":184341,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"其實生死我地係控制唔到 隨時今晚訓覺 第二朝就死左 與其每次諗起都驚餐飽 不如好好咁生存 珍惜眼前人　"},{"pid":"fd4e145515408f7c772bae2e8dc954104596b7b3","tid":184341,"uid":52938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"由細到大我都有呢個感覺 好驚死 好驚再控制唔到自己既身體 而我以後個靈魂會唔知變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21da6b98a5e99053ee76b444ff415dbaedcd3a55","tid":184341,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"死左唔洗挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想早死"},{"pid":"6052d7dbdb636f3165235f36368bf7a88d5093be","tid":184341,"uid":38726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"同你既想法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然話對現實社會感到絕望<br />\n但依然希望可以同屋企人同最愛既人繼續一齊<br />\n一齊得幾耐得幾耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525067df31e0696e5b2de41919893d361bf2a084","tid":184341,"uid":44547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:10:20.000Z","msg":"驚得過半死不活 唔生唔死？"},{"pid":"866ab4eb7546ff6edf64efe56f50611404d08945","tid":184341,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實生死我地係控制唔到 隨時今晚訓覺 第二朝就死左 與其每次諗起都驚餐飽 不如好好咁生存 珍惜眼前人　</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 所以有時做乜都好都盡量博老命等第日唔好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcd717f345c92967ac7cf1fec5a3dfbcccafabf","tid":184341,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推薦讀物<br />\nTuesdays with Morrie</blockquote><br />\n聽日就去買返本"},{"pid":"902696e9e1fdd77e32c72e6a923a22d410707d42","tid":184341,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大我都有呢個感覺 好驚死 好驚再控制唔到自己既身體 而我以後個靈魂會唔知變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係合埋眼諗到我個靈魂會鎖死係棺材出唔到黎 冇人救到你呢下真係好心寒"},{"pid":"14e914212708ccf18b7d969015f2106df8ca1990","tid":184341,"uid":78018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"會諗死左之後係咪真係咩都冇<br />\n定會有afterlife"},{"pid":"c031ebf5ce886d8884ad93365ee58176caeb881a","tid":184341,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"唔怕死<br />\n但怕痛"},{"pid":"e3483676d8ae8d149ae2251ef6b464b5b7e0a9f0","tid":184341,"uid":44016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怕死<br />\n但怕痛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> here too"},{"pid":"768e080b0a605c686bfe45f593f146161b5ede3c","tid":184341,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔怕死<br />\n但怕痛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> here too</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔痛嘅話應該一早去咗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d5df535a7445ff7cc4748f26509b4a69805de6","tid":184341,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推薦讀物<br />\nTuesdays with Morrie</blockquote><br />\n聽日就去買返本</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d3075408e06e9eb5cdbff3b41df75635acb686","tid":184341,"uid":16323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"好驚咩都要自己一個人面對"},{"pid":"480ad554be34d49bdb9618fe9545b2b1eb937d00","tid":184341,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大我都有呢個感覺 好驚死 好驚再控制唔到自己既身體 而我以後個靈魂會唔知變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係合埋眼諗到我個靈魂會鎖死係棺材出唔到黎 冇人救到你呢下真係好心寒</blockquote><br />\n咁火化撒灰呢？"},{"pid":"7066bf87d755df5aa327fb52946dbab650856dba","tid":184341,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔怕死<br />\n但怕痛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> here too</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔痛嘅話應該一早去咗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"43d4c642e74386d8a4a949443b010a47462d04bc","tid":184341,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由細到大我都有呢個感覺 好驚死 好驚再控制唔到自己既身體 而我以後個靈魂會唔知變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係合埋眼諗到我個靈魂會鎖死係棺材出唔到黎 冇人救到你呢下真係好心寒</blockquote><br />\n咁火化撒灰呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好驚燒到乜都冇 因為我覺得火化係會有感覺(雖然好唔理智）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb849e875da9020d7468ead571cbd7154b815a63","tid":184341,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}